description:
"TOO MUCH IS HAPPENING" -Not Scheana Shay's Tattoo. Danny takes us through the news cycle, which includes Bennifer reuniting, Porsha from RHOA getting engaged, and even alien encounters! Plus, he recaps the Real Housewives of Beverly Hills taglines, then onto the main event-- RHONY's Hamptons/Burning Man party that featured LOTS of healing, people on stilts, and Morley the dog.


RHOBH Taglines: 8:12ish

RHONY Recap: 14:03ish
